unittitle_ssm: Margaret Brown Dutch houses photograph collection
abstract_ssm: This collection consists of negatives and copy photographs of Dutch houses throughout New Jersey and New York states taken by Margaret Brown for two books commissioned by the Holland Society of New York: Dutch Houses in the Hudson Valley Before 1776 (1929) by Helen Wilkinson Reynolds, and Pre-Revolutionary Dutch Houses and Families in Northern New Jersey and Southern New York (1936) by Rosalie Fellows Bailey.
